thread.title_full: Totally Wicked E-liquid USA inc. reviewed by Greg Ines

author: Greg Ines
title: Greg Ines
text:
I have been off of ''tobacco cigs'' for 2 1/2 years and counting! And I thank God for ''Totally Wicked E-cig and liquid company''. Josh, a representative in Sarasota's office, fills my orders correctly, they arrive promptly, and all the inventory is in great condition.
I cannot even imagine how I could have put down the ''Marlboro Lights'' without the help of ''Totally Wicked E-cig & Liquid''.
Therefore, I hope and pray the Federal Govt's recent attacks (unattainable regulations) on the ''vaping industry'' ends very soon.
And the Feds allow them to continue to assist thousands of people ''quit smoking tobacco cigs'', like Totally Wicked is doing for me and my girlfriend.
